  "description": "additional redstone mechanics like logic gates and more",
  "body": "<h1>Additional Redstone</h1>\n<h4>adds more content to the redstone mechanics</h4>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/v31Shw5/divider-red.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n\ncurrently added logic gates:\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/dfmw4qS/basic-gates.png\" alt=\"Logic Gates\" width=\"579\" height=\"450\" /></p>\n<p>other blocks:</p>\n\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/rFM76WB/sequencer.gif\" alt=\"sequencer\" width=\"250\" height=\"188\" />\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/GtWWc3F/oscillator.gif\" alt=\"oscillator\" width=\"250\" height=\"188\" />\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/fXJ8cbD/t-flip-flop.gif\" alt=\"t flip flop\" width=\"250\" height=\"188\" />\n</p>\n\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/WHvSx50/toggle-latch.gif\" alt=\"toggle latch\" width=\"250\" height=\"188\" />\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/vzjMCQc/timer.gif\" alt=\"timer\" width=\"250\" height=\"188\" />\n</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/v31Shw5/divider-red.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n\n<p>Recipes can be found&nbsp;\n    <a title=\"Recipes\" href=\"https://github.com/tristankechlo/AdditionalRedstone/wiki/Recipes\" target=\"_blank\"\n        rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>\n</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/v31Shw5/divider-red.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n\nif you have any questions about the mod, or you want a few insights about upcoming features:\n<br>\nfeel free to join the Discord &nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a title=\"discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/bhUaWhq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VQ66pHN/Discord.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"166\" height=\"32\" />\n</a>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a title=\"discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/bhUaWhq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">link</a>",
